    <item>
      <title>新兴货币稳定，谢克尔在袭击后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/emerging-currencies-settle-as-shekel-bounces-back-after-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币企稳，因为投资者押注伊朗周末对以色列的袭击不会立即导致冲突大幅升级，其中谢克尔涨幅最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/emerging-currencies-settle-as-shekel-bounces-back-after-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:50:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击加强了与伊朗的联系股票故事：瑞银</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-15/iran-attack-reinforces-bonds-vs-equities-story-ubs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银首席策略师巴努·巴韦贾表示，伊朗对以色列发动前所未有的导弹和无人机袭击“彻底改变了市场的格局”，并强化了债券与股票的对比。巴韦贾在彭博电视上表示：“相对于一些股票市场的预期市盈率达 20 至 21 倍，10 年期美国国债 4.50% 的利率相当有吸引力。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-15/iran-attack-reinforces-bonds-vs-equities-story-ubs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:48:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利表示，阿迪达斯可以从耐克的创新斗争中受益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/adidas-could-benefit-from-nike-s-innovation-struggles-morgan-stanley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利分析师表示，由于竞争对手耐克公司在产品创新方面陷入困境，运动鞋时尚趋势正在向阿迪达斯公司倾斜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/adidas-could-benefit-from-nike-s-innovation-struggles-morgan-stanley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在选举前查获创纪录的 5.57 亿美元非法现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-hauls-record-557-million-in-illicit-cash-before-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度选举委员会在投票前没收了创纪录的 465 亿卢比（5.57 亿美元）非法资金和物品，超过了 2019 年整个选举的收缴量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-hauls-record-557-million-in-illicit-cash-before-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度3月份贸易逆差收窄至11个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-march-trade-gap-narrows-to-11-month-low-on-low-import-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度3月份的贸易逆差收窄至11个月低点，原因是该国控制了进口费用，而全球需求的复苏有助于保持出口稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-march-trade-gap-narrows-to-11-month-low-on-low-import-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于避险买盘减弱，通胀担忧让债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末前席卷市场的国债买盘正在平息，人们希望伊朗和以色列之间的冲突现在能够平息，人们的注意力又回到了困扰世界经济的通胀压力上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:26:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
